{"tid":1123091,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"兑吧(01753-HK)招股 入場費約3272.65港元","createTime":"2019-04-24T09:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T05:52:50.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a39e58a8767242fb9d991e390ba9f36ec4479123","tid":1123091,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:19:05.000Z","msg":"今日公佈於聯交所主板上市計劃，公司計劃此次發售逾1.11億股股份，其中約10%於本港公開發售，近90%作國際配售。公開發售將於明天（4月24日）開始直至4月29日結束。招股價介乎6港元至8.1港元。每手400股，入場費約3272.65港元。招銀國際和匯豐擔任聯席保薦人，預計公司5月7日於聯交所主板掛牌。<br />\n<br />\n以發售價中位數7.05港元計，預計公司將籌得款項淨額約7.033億港元，其中37%將用於研究和增強技術能力；25%用於改善公司銷售及市場推廣能力；25%用於投資及收購與公司業務及技術相關或互補的公司及企業；8%用於改善運營能力；以及10%用於營運資金及一般公司用途。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2003及1917都升唔少，有冇人玩？"},{"pid":"6ff042910ee10578ada213fd1fea2a5d925dcb72","tid":1123091,"uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"有d 貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40220306732f2d933334e318154976ca83b9593d","tid":1123091,"uid":71738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:59:49.000Z","msg":"3手試下先"},{"pid":"8c5581eabcdcb25b4c62f189d161e67b678e542b","tid":1123091,"uid":219986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40220306732f2d933334e318154976ca83b9593d","tid":1123091,"uid":71738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:59:49.000Z","msg":"3手試下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T21:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb70f6a09e1e3eb7d1abfbf0f33d54fd05d79a11","tid":1123091,"uid":151241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T03:17:34.000Z","msg":"3手+1"},{"pid":"6f8b6d91cf1da9aec29001ca622cf5d7864b0cd1","tid":1123091,"uid":224106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"間野做乜業務？"},{"pid":"eb36ed6a9d3001c1e615a15afbd4b1d